{"tw": {"3903800": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "迷失在太空廢墟中的母親", "steam_appid": 3903800, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/483773b31c506a32d55ca198e3fff99f.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/483773b31c506a32d55ca198e3fff99f.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年空與摯友太郎，以及母親美月正搭乘一艘太空穿梭機。在前往一顆近來廣受歡迎的度假行星途中，三人心情愉快，卻突然遭遇意外。此時，穿梭機附近出現了一個小型黑洞，船員們連同他們一同失蹤。當空甦醒時，發現自己身處於一座神秘的廢棄殖民地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現在，空必須在陌生的太空廢墟中穿行，重新與母親和太郎會合，並蒐集逃離的線索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他是否能及時找出真相，並在下一場災難發生前逃離這座廢棄殖民地？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/913b7c50c3d4cf623261c7c9d281099d.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/913b7c50c3d4cf623261c7c9d281099d.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身空探索廢棄殖民地，尋找推動劇情的線索。設法進入殖民地的不同區域，穿梭於各樓層、管道與坍塌的空間。與太郎和美月不時會合，共同規劃後續行動，做出必要的抉擇以求生存並找到逃離的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著劇情推進，你也能回到先前的地點，解鎖更多隱藏場景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/55ccb975d18db8f9316542148ee50e49.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/55ccb975d18db8f9316542148ee50e49.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/81d756d0805a4ac396522fdd83e0aee3.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/81d756d0805a4ac396522fdd83e0aee3.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/f39651d232818e10bc52ac376f47980b.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/f39651d232818e10bc52ac376f47980b.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/80d241f5c47f8fae0901551054a0e325.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/80d241f5c47f8fae0901551054a0e325.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>調查與探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索廢棄的殖民地，從備忘錄、報告與留下的物品中尋找線索。觀察環境、修復故障的機械，幫助你進入原本封鎖或危險的區域。解開一些簡單的謎題，以前往被隔絕的場所。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>意想不到的遭遇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這座廢棄的殖民地中，除了空、美月與太郎外，沒有任何活著的身影，但他們卻始終無法真正會合。這裡是否還有其他倖存者？你會遇見幽靈、外星人，還是奇異的生物？探索每個角落，找出真相吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>謎題與線索蒐集</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著探索的深入，你將透過線索或遺留物品來解鎖新的地點。這些謎題的提示都隱藏在遊戲過程之中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>額外內容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成遊戲後，將會解鎖一段特別的故事，可從主選單進入體驗。</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/483773b31c506a32d55ca198e3fff99f.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/483773b31c506a32d55ca198e3fff99f.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年空與摯友太郎，以及母親美月正搭乘一艘太空穿梭機。在前往一顆近來廣受歡迎的度假行星途中，三人心情愉快，卻突然遭遇意外。此時，穿梭機附近出現了一個小型黑洞，船員們連同他們一同失蹤。當空甦醒時，發現自己身處於一座神秘的廢棄殖民地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現在，空必須在陌生的太空廢墟中穿行，重新與母親和太郎會合，並蒐集逃離的線索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他是否能及時找出真相，並在下一場災難發生前逃離這座廢棄殖民地？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/913b7c50c3d4cf623261c7c9d281099d.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/913b7c50c3d4cf623261c7c9d281099d.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身空探索廢棄殖民地，尋找推動劇情的線索。設法進入殖民地的不同區域，穿梭於各樓層、管道與坍塌的空間。與太郎和美月不時會合，共同規劃後續行動，做出必要的抉擇以求生存並找到逃離的方法。</p><p c