68618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/80d241f5c47f8fae0901551054a0e325.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>調查與探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索廢棄的殖民地，從備忘錄、報告與留下的物品中尋找線索。觀察環境、修復故障的機械，幫助你進入原本封鎖或危險的區域。解開一些簡單的謎題，以前往被隔絕的場所。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>意想不到的遭遇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這座廢棄的殖民地中，除了空、美月與太郎外，沒有任何活著的身影，但他們卻始終無法真正會合。這裡是否還有其他倖存者？你會遇見幽靈、外星人，還是奇異的生物？探索每個角落，找出真相吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>謎題與線索蒐集</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著探索的深入，你將透過線索或遺留物品來解鎖新的地點。這些謎題的提示都隱藏在遊戲過程之中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>額外內容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成遊戲後，將會解鎖一段特別的故事，可從主選單進入體驗。</p>", "short_description": "扮演少年空，被困於一座廢棄的太空殖民地之中。探索坍塌的通道、解開謎題、尋找線索，並努力與母親美月以及好友太郎重逢。他們必須同心協力，找到回家的方法。在下一場災難降臨之前，他們能順利逃離嗎？", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 繁體中文, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/838334279516f37398c0789fee5a24f0ee0b3d46/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1768618319", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/680f2a85384f04f812b40537e63062ac509ccee0/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1768618319", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/680f2a85384f04f812b40537e63062ac509ccee0/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1768618319", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Uno"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 18800, "final": 18800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 188"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 1 月 16 日"}}}}, "us": {"3903800": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Mom Stolen in Space", "steam_appid": 3903800, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/e6943919d9bab35ddd682a8106c71be4.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/e6943919d9bab35ddd682a8106c71be4.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young boy named Sora, his best friend Tarou, and Sora's mother Mitsuki are aboard a space shuttle. During a galactic trip to a resort planet that’s been growing in popularity lately, the three are in high spirits, but something terrible happens. At the same time, a small black hole appears near the shuttle. The crew, including the three caught up in it, goes missing. Sora wakes up in a mysterious abandoned colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now Sora has to navigate the unfamiliar space, regroup with his mom and Tarou, and gather clues on how to get out of this strange place. Will Sora find the clues in time and escape from this abandoned colony before another disaster befalls them? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/770c6595da0eccead080ef752346ba0c.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/770c6595da0eccead080ef752346ba0c.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the abandoned colony as Sora and look for clues to progress the story. Find ways to access different areas in the colony, navigating your way around various floors, ducts, and collapsed areas. Regroup with Tarou and Mitsuki from time to time to plan ahead and do what is necessary to survive and find a way out. As you progress through the story, revisit previous locations to unlock additional scenes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/67afdb43cb93a718528c5bd8ebb42e1a.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/67afdb43cb93a718528c5bd8ebb42e1a.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/c01f762c641b7473193d7504d04f9f1d.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/c01f762c641b7473193d7504d04f9f1d.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/b40af8c49794772a687f2b982db77563.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/b40af8c49794772a687f2b982db77563.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/4a756a9a460bfb706e85c9a1f2bb2de9.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/4a756a9a460bfb706e85c9a1f2bb2de9.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Investigation and Exploration</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the abandoned colony, find clues from items left behind by the people who lived and worked here. Observe the environment and fix broken machines, so that they help you progress through previously locked or dangerous areas. Solve some simple puzzles to access sealed-off places.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unexpected Encounters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is not a single living soul in this abandoned colony except Sora, Mitsuki, and Tarou, who somehow cannot seem to meet up with each other. But perhaps there are other survivors here? Will you encounter a ghost, an alien, or some strange animal? Explore every corner to find out.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Puzzles and Clue Gathering</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore all areas, you will unlock access to new locations using clues or items left behind. Hints for these puzzles are provided within the gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bonus Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon completing the game, a special story to play through will be unlocked, accessible from the main menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/e6943919d9bab35ddd682a8106c71be4.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/e6943919d9bab35ddd682a8106c71be4.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young boy named Sora, his best friend Tarou, and Sora's mother Mitsuki are aboard a space shuttle. During a galactic trip to a resort planet that’s been growing in popularity lately, the three are in high spirits, but something terrible happens. At the same time, a small black hole appears near the shuttle. The crew, including the three caught up in it, goes missing. Sora wakes up in a mysterious abandoned colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now Sora has to navigate the unfamiliar space, regroup with his mom and Tarou, and gather clues on how to get out of this strange place. Will Sora find the clues in time and escape from this abandoned colony before another disaster befalls them? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/770c6595da0eccead080ef752346ba0c.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/770c6595da0eccead080ef752346ba0c.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the abandoned colony as Sora and look for clues to progress the story. Find ways to access different areas in the colony, navigating your way around various floors, ducts, and collapsed areas. Regroup with Tarou and Mitsuki from time to time to plan ahead and do what is necessary to survive and find a way out. As you progress through the story, revisit previous locations to unlock additional scenes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/67afdb43cb93a718528c5bd8ebb42e1a.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/67afdb43cb93a718528c5bd8ebb42e1a.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/c01f762c641b7473193d7504d04f9f1d.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/c01f762c641b7473193d7504d04f9f1d.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/b40af8c49794772a687f2b982db77563.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/b40af8c49794772a687f2b982db77563.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/4a756a9a460bfb706e85c9a1f2bb2de9.poster.avif?t=1768618319\" width=780 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/extras/4a756a9a460bfb706e85c9a1f2bb2de9.webm?t=1768618319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Investigation and Exploration</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the abandoned colony, find clues from items left behind by the people who lived and worked here. Observe the environment and fix broken machines, so that they help you progress through previously locked or dangerous areas. Solve some simple puzzles to access sealed-off places.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unexpected Encounters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is not a single living soul in this abandoned colony except Sora, Mitsuki, and Tarou, who somehow cannot seem to meet up with each other. But perhaps there are other survivors here? Will you encounter a ghost, an alien, or some strange animal? Explore every corner to find out.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Puzzles and Clue Gathering</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore all areas, you will unlock access to new locations using clues or items left behind. Hints for these puzzles are provided within the gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bonus Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon completing the game, a special story to play through will be unlocked, accessible from the main menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "Play as Sora, a boy stranded in an abandoned space colony. Explore collapsed passages, solve puzzles, and uncover clues while trying to reunite with his mother Mitsuki and friend Tarou. Together, they must find a way home. Can they escape before another disaster strikes?", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese<strong>*</strong>, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Korean<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/a1d21c498b78aee2cd24d79f4c09b2636abf72ba/header.jpg?t=1768618319", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/26e592bde173dfcddcb0b6d9f745ff10eac8ec10/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1768618319", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3903800/26e592bde173dfcddcb0b6d9f745ff10eac8ec10/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1768618319", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Uno"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "USD", "initial": 999, "final": 999, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "$9.99"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "Single-player"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam Achievements"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam Cloud"}, {"id": 62, "description": "Family Sharing"}], "genres": [{"id": 